title: Hour 3 – It’s the Eagles world; we’re just living in it!
itunes:title: Hour 3 – It’s the Eagles world; we’re just living in it!
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, Jason Smith and Mike Harmon debate if the Philadelphia Eagles are the best team in the NFC. Fox Sports 1 NBA Analyst Ric Bucher tells you where the Kyrie Irving situation goes from here. And the guys give you their BIG bold predictions for Week 9 in the NFL.
